listing.name: Import to Board (JSON) for Trello
listing.description:
Import to Board (JSON) for Trello is a versatile Trello Power-Up designed to supercharge your workflow. It enables you to import board data that has been exported in JSON format, providing a seamless way to restore or duplicate boards. Additionally, it equips you with the functionality to archive all lists on your current board with ease. This Power-Up is perfect for teams looking to streamline their processes and maintain organization across multiple projects.

Try Import to Board (JSON) for Trello free for 14 days.


## Import to Board (JSON) for Trello allows you to 

![Import To Board](https://world-clock-for-trello.netlify.app/images/import_to_board.gif)

### Import json data to board 

✅ Board name  
✅ Board description  
✅ Lists  
✅ Labels  
✅ Cards  
✅ Labels  
✅ Checklists  

### Archive all lists and unarchive lists

### Import selected lists

![Import Selected Lists](https://world-clock-for-trello.netlify.app/images/import_selected_lists.gif)

### JSON format 

The JSON format we support is exported through the Trello export data function:

![Print and Export](https://world-clock-for-trello.netlify.app/images/BoardOptionsExportJSON.png)

More details:

- [Export data from Trello](https://support.atlassian.com/trello/docs/exporting-data-from-trello/)
- [Making sense of Trello's JSON export](https://support.atlassian.com/trello/docs/making-sense-of-trellos-json-export/)

## Protect your data

Import to Board (JSON) for Trello is committed to managing your data securely and transparently. We do not store any of your content — in fact, we never even see it. We will never share your personal information.

## Support when you need it

If you need help with anything, please email us at [wbohome@outlook.com](mailto:wbohome@outlook.com). We'll respond quickly and help any way we can.

## Pricing

You have a trial period of 14 days.After that, it requires a small fee: $1.99/month or $19.90/year per board.
